  "synopsis": "S-class Hunter Kim Yiyoung can’t wait to leave the novel she woke up in. She gets the chance after defeating the story’s final boss, but instead of returning home, she’s sent into another novel! Yiyoung becomes Lady Renee Markious, a petty villainess who’s just been framed for murder. Fortunately, Yiyoung has a secret weapon nobody knows about… her skills from her past life! Can Yiyoung clear Renee’s name and find her way back to her own world? Or will she be trapped in this tale for good?\n\n*Source: Tapas*",
